# LeetCode-face-0108.零矩阵  
2022.09.30  
难度：中等  
编写一种算法，若M × N矩阵中某个元素为0，则将其所在的行与列清零。  
> ## 示例
> ![图1][image]
```c
typedef struct point{
    int x;
    int y;
}P;
void setZeroes(int** matrix, int matrixSize, int* matrixColSize){
    int i = 0, j = 0, k = 0, nums = 0;
    int col = *matrixColSize;
    int size = matrixSize * col;
    P * points = (P *)malloc(sizeof(P) * size);
    for(k = 0; k < size; k++){
        points[k].x = -1;
        points[k].y = -1;
    }
    for(i = 0; i < size; i++){
        printf("points[%d].x:%d, points[%d].y:%d\n", i, points[i].x, i, points[i].y);
    }
    k = 0;
    for(i = 0; i < matrixSize; i++){
        for(j = 0; j < col; j++){
            if(matrix[i][j] == 0){
                points[k].x = i;
                points[k++].y = j;
                nums++;
            }
        }
    }
    for(i = 0; i < size; i++){
        printf("points[%d].x:%d, points[%d].y:%d\n", i, points[i].x, i, points[i].y);
    }
    for(i = 0; i < nums; i++){
        for(j = 0; j < matrixSize; j++) matrix[j][points[i].y] = 0;
        for(j = 0; j < col; j++) matrix[points[i].x][j] = 0;
    }
}
```
# 简单模拟题（宫水三叶）
```java
class Solution {
    public void setZeroes(int[][] mat) {
        int n = mat.length, m = mat[0].length;
        boolean[] rows = new boolean[n], cols = new boolean[m];
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {
                if (mat[i][j] == 0) rows[i] = cols[j] = true;
            }
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {
                if (rows[i] || cols[j]) mat[i][j] = 0;
            }
        }
    }
}
```
